title: Socrates: Man and Myth
itunes:subtitle: Philosophy Now Radio Show #24
itunes:author: Philosophy Now
description: Grant Bartley from Philosophy Now discusses Socrates, his ideas and role in Western philosophy, with  M.M. McCabe from King’s College London, and Tim Chappell from the Open University. First broadcast on 31 January 2012 on Resonance FM.
